YELLOW FEVER IN ASIA (2)
==========================

In India it is thought that Yellow Fever is not found because of the
presence of DENGUE Fever.

We have started thinking about the Indian Situation and feel that
eradicating DENGUE may bring in Yellow Fever.

Ajit Maru

Ajit Maru, Ph.D.
Scientist - III (Epidemiology)
National Dairy Development Board
Anand Gujarat
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
{- The preventive aspects of endemic dengue has long been the traditional
view on why yellow fever is absent from Asia. MH-J Act-Mod]
